title: WEED by Sanjay Gupta MD - CNN Report 10Aug13 1080p AC-3

WEED - CNN Special Investigative Report - Dr. Sanjay Gupta MD - Aug10, 2013



This current and balanced report on Medical Marijuana was recently aired on CNN.

It mostly covers the breakthrough medical treatments that are just now being discovered. It includes an in-depth report on the treatment of childhood epilepsy and the development of specialized strains of Weed developed strictly for their medicinal value. It also covers the current and changing federal and state laws. Lastly, it discusses several negative problems that can result if marijuana is used at too young an age.
